request.description:
The `/logout` endpoint is an HTTP POST request used to log out the user. Upon successful execution, the server returns a JSON response with a status code of 200 and a content type of `application/json`. The response schema for this request is as follows:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "status": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "data": {
            "type": "null"
        }
    }
}

 ```
